reviewText: I did not realize that it came from another country.. So when I got it,, none of these DVDs did not work at all.. I was very very upset.. Which is not your fault at all..  I will always continue to order from Amazon.. When I tried to ship them back,, I was told it would cost a lot of money to ship them,,,so I just got rid of them. It was not worth the money.. But everything else that I have ever gotten from Amazon,, has been a success for me.. So I will continue to make my orders.. This order was just unfortunate..
